{"tid":1088282,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"朝早食咩野都好易肚痛","createTime":"2019-04-02T02:41:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-02T07:58:23.000Z","uid":229034,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1a10604e59d512a16fafa7f9eb4e8438c9f3a700","tid":1088282,"uid":229034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T02:41:56.000Z","msg":"朝早只可以食少少野，例如一個包<br />\n食飽少少好似食一個大家樂早餐都會肚痛<br />\n仲有一定唔飲得奶類製品，一飲即痾<br />\n呢個情況只係朝早出現<br />\nLunch dinner 食咩都冇事<br />\n有冇人都係咁？"},{"pid":"34a2ba2675f41464aec41864da8ed8ae8a02b2a0","tid":1088282,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T02:44:25.000Z","msg":"食乜都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3192ca309684435422f24a856521affd725bfd61","tid":1088282,"uid":27433,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T02:44:30.000Z","msg":"我返工一定唔食得早餐，會嘔<br />\n飲奶仲會肚痛<br />\n但去旅行或放假就冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bf83d5f798894ff261ac04bef372af1d658cbb9","tid":1088282,"uid":140726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T02:44:40.000Z","msg":"習慣咗就冇事"},{"pid":"ad827c89dcf0646285b704076ee58ab43eddf03d","tid":1088282,"uid":183113,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T02:45:10.000Z","msg":"因為空肚食嘢"},{"pid":"444b25cd3af5bc2895c0bb63d2f83f7e4d34efb4","tid":1088282,"uid":144201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T02:45:59.000Z","msg":"我，由小學都依加出嚟做野都係，應該係生理時鐘set咗係朝早<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf0d1a2cc6cdb39cbc3996b11a45154092dfe1cc","tid":1088282,"uid":141148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T02:46:04.000Z","msg":"太油咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3e65fb858bfda4f6d2c0a47107858f4bfcb939e","tid":1088282,"uid":17453,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T02:47